(12, 6, 'iPhone 14 series', 'iphone-14-series', 'iPhone 14 Series chính hãng - Mới 100%, giá tốt', '<p>Mua iPhone 14 series chính hãng: iPhone 14, 14 Plus, 14 Pro, 14 Pro Max. Giá tốt, bảo hành đầy đủ.</p>', 'iPhone 14 series, iPhone 14, iPhone 14 Plus, iPhone 14 Pro, iPhone 14 Pro Max', 'https://d2di287i5rkooq.cloudfront.net/categories/12/image/cayDKKkGJlel0YvR5tsPGITvunmiUaG0jQuIIIbw.webp', 'https://d2di287i5rkooq.cloudfront.net/categories/12/banner/XpYiSbHtjRhmynYmXF30gQyCnY8zGMKluJaMqHrN.jpg', '2025-06-22 23:45:22', '2025-07-09 09:54:02'),
